race.description: Team Aidan Market 23 Nov Country Boosted Mdn Plt
race.comment: SO SAIN (9) has done early work to find the lead from wide gates at her last two appearances and dug deep to be narrowly denied on each occasion. Draws the fence this time and is rock-hard fit. This looks her big chance to grab a well-deserved win. RUFUS ATTICUS (7) missed the kick before making late ground to finish midfield when resuming over 1300m at Coonamble last time out. Draws closer than eight for the first time in two preps. Can play a big role. MCCOSKER (3) wasn't expected to do much on debut last start over 1200m at Murwillumbah but he did well to stick on for third after showing pace from the outset. Winkers go on. Winning hope with a bit of natural improvement to come. RAINSITPOURS (5) isn't the most reliable conveyance but if he brings his best a top three finish is on the cards. Keep tabs on HIGHWIRE GIRL (10) wearing blinkers for the first time.
